author: @duckbufflehead6294
text:
For the week ending on November 23, 2024 Rosé and Bruno Mars’ smash hit “APT.” rose to a new peak on Billboard’s Pop Airplay chart, which measures weekly plays on mainstream Top 40 radio stations across the United States. In its fourth consecutive week on the chart, “APT.” jumped to No. 20.

“APT.” also remained No. 1 on both the Billboard’s Global 200 and Global Excl. U.S. charts for the fourth week in a row—making Rosé the first female K-pop soloist ever to top the Global 200 for four weeks.

Additionally, “APT.” climbed back up to No. 13 in its fourth week on Billboard’s Hot 100, which ranks the most popular songs in the United States. The song currently holds the record for the highest ranking ever achieved by a female K-pop artist—including groups—on the Hot 100, where it debuted at No. 8!

author: @aioedk8611
text:
La gente es tan asquerosamente hipócrita, el año pasado se comieron vivas a blackpink, y ahora ¿resulta que son legendarias? 
¿Al menos vieron la presentación completa de Le Sserafim y todos los elogios que recibieron?, ¿O solamente se basan en los clips de SEGUNDOS que andan por ahí con el objetivo de dejar mal a este grupo? 
Son todos una bola de tontos, porque blackpink lo hizo bien desde el principio, no es justo que solo vengan aquí para hablar mal de alguien más, porque así como blackpink cometió errores en sus presentaciones el año pasado, lo mismo pasa con le sserafim este año, y también le pasa a TODOS los grupos que se presentan en vivo, por dios! Son humanos, no pueden ser perfectos la mayoría de tiempo que pasan en pantallas. 
Cada uno hace lo mejor que puede con la preparación que tiene.
Lo mejor es que ustedes se corten los dedos para que dejen de escribir estupideces. ¿No pueden solamente disfrutar de la presentación que les gusta y ya?

text:
근본과 급조의 차이 같음
와이지가 아무리 개떡같은 회사여도  골수대형엔터 답게 애초에 라이브 실력 없으면 뽑질 않음. 그래서 와이지 가수들 데뷔 무대 보면 표정 망가지는거 신경도 안쓰고 입 빡빡 벌리면서 라이브부터 함. 
반면 대기업인 그곳은 회사가 급성장한  만큼 아이돌도 급하게 뽑아낸것 같은 느낌이 강하게 듦. 급하게 뽑아야 하니 라이브  실력은 후순위. 비주얼과 이미지만 맞추기에 급급함. 이렇게 마케팅 위주로  급조된 모습들은 코첼라 같은 대형 무대에서 그 역량이 뽀록난다고 생각함...

author: @ShielaTV
text:
That was spectacular. Love their stage presence. I don't like their live before because I feel they are lacking in stage presence and their performance are drowned by the crowd, like they can't control they viewers. But now, uhm! 😘👌❤️ I'm liking every part of each members. They have their own style and presence that makes them who they are despite being in a group. Now I can say that in my heart, they are now equal to my first favorite k-group which is 2ne1.

1. 2NE1 (2nd gen)
2. G-Idle (2nd gen/3rd?)
3. BlackPink
4. Exid (2nd gen/3rd?)
5. Girls Generation

It's just that... No one has yet to replace CL in terms of her vocals for me. Her voice is just powerful, the down side is, she over power her own members. 😅
